  "texts": [
    "These networks have demonstrated the capability to significantly augment the accuracy of image classification, ushering in a new era of possibilities in the realm of plant disease identification.",
    "Within this context, this section of the discourse aims to elucidate the various deep learning techniques that have been harnessed by researchers to tackle the intricate challenge of plant disease identification.",
    "In a seminal work by Mohanty et al.",
    "[3], the prowess of the AlexNet architecture was harnessed to train and classify plant diseases that were previously unencountered.",
    "The implications were profound, as this approach exhibited promising results."
